reviews.text: Classic Italian restaurant. Not that I've been to many. Food and service was great. I also loved the little grocery corner.

Knew this restaurant since 2015, the food was good at first (I would give 4 stars), but may be due to the change in their chef team, the taste becomes  different and more improvement is surely needed. I personally like their deli products and some italian groceries for sales at the spot.
long time establishment to cater for Italian food lover
It was much better a couple of years ago... seems to me there must be a new owner?
